{"name":"Midnight Combat Suit","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/vest-leather-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3uiNX8VLV5Ac89zC"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This low-profile synfiber suit was a standard-issue item for Wayfinder operatives on long missions behind enemy lines, providing a good balance of comfort, concealability, weight and resistance against small-caliber weapons. The dark, optically semi-adaptive weave makes this suit an excellent choice for night-time missions.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":1,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":true,"armor":3,"ward":0,"evasion":1,"magicArmor":3,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401201181,"modifiedTime":1763401201181,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"0HjR0nvkwY202pny"}
{"name":"Black Leather Combat Suit","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/robe-layered-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uuFcYM459m2TD6jD"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"","bulk":2,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":4,"ward":0,"evasion":2,"magicArmor":4,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401189810,"modifiedTime":1763401189810,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"0tyfD5Gw8EKeZqaa"}
{"name":"Bolted-on Armor Plates","type":"armor","img":"icons/environment/traps/pressure-plate.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5kjlVSDMT5BasOSK"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-f50bbe35-7fff-33aa-a6ed-09d080914ff8\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&ldquo;No, Bepi, it&rsquo;s not a </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">kludge</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, it&rsquo;s </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">expedient engineering</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, okay&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>","bulk":2,"charge":0,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":3,"ward":0,"evasion":-1,"magicArmor":0,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401193903,"modifiedTime":1763401193903,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"1vUP5FCA53DKyjlT"}
{"name":"Dragon Guard Power Armor","type":"armor","img":"icons/armor/power_armor_icon.png","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.v1bEcWWYKtBHwqah"}},"system":{"tier":3,"name":"","description":"<p><em>The powered armor of the Fraternity of Iron is an imposing frame of steel, painted in a fiery red lacquer and trimmed with gold. The dragon crest of the order gleams from the chestplate and the epaulets.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Using this suit of power armor in powered mode requires the <em>Powered Proficiency </em>advance. In powered mode, this suit provides the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+8 Bulk</li>\n<li>Resist 10 Thermal</li>\n<li>Autostabilizer</li>\n<li>Rebreather</li>\n<li>1000 MPU mod power supply</li>\n</ul>","bulk":5,"charge":1,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":true,"armor":15,"ward":0,"evasion":-4,"magicArmor":10,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401195619,"modifiedTime":1763401195619,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"CjfpfYrRpLgPh4qm"}
{"name":"Zahak-Pattern Serpent Frame","type":"armor","img":"icons/creatures/reptiles/snake-poised-white.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.XZMh0h26WsluFgJj"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-3a678d15-7fff-42e3-f015-2bdda35dd661\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Movement Speed +2</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Effects:</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> You treat difficult terrain as treacherous terrain, and steps are difficult terrain for you.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">You gain +3 successes on attempts to grapple and you can grapple creatures one size larger than you. When you are grappling, you are considered to have your hands free.</span></p>","bulk":3,"charge":3,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":8,"ward":0,"evasion":0,"magicArmor":5,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401210569,"modifiedTime":1763401210569,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"ObKfS249oco8iXZZ"}
