{"name":"Flak Vest","type":"armor","img":"icons/armor/Mk_III_Flak_Vest.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.f0gTFN8xAAxySvao"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>A sturdy bit of armor, great against bullets and fragments.</p>","bulk":2,"charge":0,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":6,"ward":0,"evasion":-2,"magicArmor":1,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401197474,"modifiedTime":1763401197474,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"Qy4jGCpTf1BCCeRc"}
{"name":"Amulet of Undead Warding","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/neck/amulet-geometric-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.fCDTEL9DsV8qCoCU"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>This amulet grants you 3 armor against attacks by Undead creatures.</p>","bulk":0,"charge":1,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":0,"ward":0,"evasion":0,"magicArmor":0,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401187754,"modifiedTime":1763401187754,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"S3uaqwCcujgVc6Fn"}
{"name":"Hunter-Killer Combat Suit","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-layered-leather-studded-brown.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.orMIwadsMxxjfAQY"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"","bulk":0.5,"charge":0,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":4,"ward":0,"evasion":1,"magicArmor":3,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401199230,"modifiedTime":1763401199230,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"UJn1XZc2XS580wNM"}
{"name":"Mistwalker Robes","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/robe-layered-blue.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.N9YbEcP0QeCAFakl"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>These heavy robes are frequently worn by the magic users of the Order of the Lantern. The interlaced fibers of synweave and wool seem to almost repel the ambient mist, granting the wearer exceptional protection against harmful magical influences. The downside of this property is that the robes inhibit the wearer's own use of magic.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":2,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":3,"ward":0,"evasion":1,"magicArmor":6,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401203106,"modifiedTime":1763401203106,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"kZToilQCHjgCirgQ"}
{"name":"Warmage Robes","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/robe-layered-red.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.WprDOc1MuvbIRAE4"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p>A style of robes worn by many war-wizards during the Old War. They do a very good job of keeping their wearer alive for their weight, but the amount of magical energy that must be controlled to make proper use of them is nontrivial.</p>","bulk":1,"charge":3,"class":"medium","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":5,"ward":0,"evasion":1,"magicArmor":8,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401208890,"modifiedTime":1763401208890,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"skf4JQYdbOrUb6Kg"}
{"name":"Sudassi-Pattern Construct Frame","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-banded-steel-studded.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.XiFA11E7QnxZ9Tfc"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p>This heavy, nearly two meters tall construct frame was mass-produced in the war-foundries of the Iron Heirs to feed the immaculate legions' voracious demand for new bodies, as countless Ironhands were destroyed on the battlefield every day. The composite Ferrotensite-Synplate structure affords excellent protection against even large-caliber fire and can support mount points for heavy weaponry, but makes the frame awkward to move in.</p>","bulk":5,"charge":2,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":7,"ward":0,"evasion":-2,"magicArmor":5},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401207190,"modifiedTime":1763401207190,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"t1m2qAZb2f6PhLFy"}
{"name":"Sudassi-Pattern Artillery Frame","type":"armor","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/grenade-round.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.BqRZT6J1lCYioT7r"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-61bca87d-7fff-3885-04bc-618d2a071841\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Movement Speed -2</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Effects: </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Your land speed changes to a fly speed (hover). If you fire a heavy weapon without bracing, the recoil pushes you back 3 squares. If you move during your turn, you can brace as a free action, but you must spend a minor action to undo your firing anchors before you can move again.</span></p>","bulk":5,"charge":3,"class":"heavy","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":8,"ward":0,"evasion":-2,"magicArmor":11,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.1","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1763401205174,"modifiedTime":1763401205174,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"yA3wT4lpecpEBwTt"}
{"name":"Coldlight Robes","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/robe-layered-white.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Masterwork Light Armor, Tier 6 &bull; Robe, Ice, Light</strong></p>\n<p><em>The priests of Iyalan specialized in spinning the silver light of the moon into magical threads, cold to the touch as silver, yet sheer as silk. The ceremonial garments woven from these magical threads were among their most prized treasures.</em></p>\n<p>This set of robes has the following traits:</p>\n<p><strong>Moonsilver:&nbsp;</strong>These robes grant the wearer a +3 bonus to casting ice and moonlight spells.</p>\n<p><strong>Aura of Cold:</strong> In battle, these robes generate a vortex of cold air. The vortex is an aura 1; any creature that enters or starts its turn in the aura takes 20 cold damage. Suppressing or reactivating this aura is a free action, but can only be done once per round.</p>\n<p><strong>Sheer Reflection:&nbsp;</strong>In moonlight, the robes become suffused with magical power. Their bonuses to Ward and Evasion increase to +30 and +5, respectively; additionally, the casting bonuses granted increase to +5 each.&nbsp;</p>","bulk":1,"charge":4,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":10,"ward":25,"evasion":2,"quantity":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5lp6XCFgtGo90uln"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767465482995,"modifiedTime":1774473908612,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"G9Q8ntzRQL4wRRS8"}
{"name":"Moonlight Combat Suit","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-gorget-steel-white.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Masterwork Light Armor, Tier 6 &bull; Moonlight</strong></p>\n<p><em>Branded with the sigil of the Heirs, this masterwork combat suit was made for one of the Blood Moon's Oathpledged. Her blessing upon it grants the wearer phenomenal advantages if he fights by her light.</em></p>\n<p>This suit is a&nbsp;<em>+2 Lightbender Deflecting&nbsp;</em>Synscale combat suit. Apart from its normal equipment bonuses, it grants the following traits:</p>\n<p><strong>Masterwork Synscale:&nbsp;</strong>The overlapping plates of ultra-thin material not only privide excellent protection, but also n excellent job of hiding the wearer's physical and magical emissions. The wearer of this suit gains a +4d bonus to subterfuge checks to avoid detection by any senses, including lifesense and magicsense, other than smell.</p>\n<p><strong>Light Bender: </strong>This suit of armor bends the light around it. When fighting in bright light, its evasion bonus increases by 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Deflecting</strong>: The synscales of this suit are magically treated. When the wearer is targeted by an area-effect spell or magical ability, the suit grants the wearer light cover against that spell or ability.</p>\n<p><strong>Moonlight Blessing:&nbsp;</strong>In moonlight, the power of the Blood Moon courses through this suit. As a 1 AP action, the wearer can choose to spend 2 EP; he becomes invisible to all senses for the scene or while he remains in the moonlight.&nbsp;</p>","bulk":2,"charge":3,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":18,"ward":10,"evasion":3,"quantity":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zmsGRhQA9tFu6VY6"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767465162982,"modifiedTime":1774473912141,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"qf7tbAjqZc7Ndtto"}
{"name":"Vanth's Sypharion","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-metal-scaled-grey.webp","system":{"tier":6,"name":"","description":"<p><strong>Legendary Light Armor, Tier 6</strong></p>\n<p><em>This set of armor was once owned by Vanth, shadow of the midnight gates. Seemingly composed of the actual black scales of some monstrous serpent riveted onto a sturdy synfiber backing, it does not provide the protection of armor made from heavier materias, but its magical powers more than make up for it.&nbsp;<br><br></em>This unique set of armor grants the following traits:</p>\n<p><strong>Shadowscale:</strong> The scales of this suit attenuate the presence of the wearer. The wearer gains a +5d bonus to subterfuge checks made to avoid detection by any senses, including supernatural ones. Its evasion bonus increases to +5 in low light of darkness.</p>\n<p><strong>Keratin Point:&nbsp;</strong>The scales on this armor are artfully arranged so that they present very few flat surfaces, deflecting a great proportion of incoming thrusts entirely. Thr wearer of this armor gains cover against attacks dealing piercing damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Slough Off:</strong> When damaged, the armor can expel a thin layer of skin, like the moult of a snake, buying its wearer valuable time. Once per round, when hit by an attack, a wearer possessing the <em>Fey Jaunt</em> ability can use it to escape the attack, leaving behind a husk of sloughed-off skin. If they do so, the attack affects the husk instead.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","bulk":1,"charge":3,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":15,"ward":15,"evasion":3,"quantity":null},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AtcTfYoPKstTsgW4"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1767464486509,"modifiedTime":1774473914743,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"TXvqzctfFSJKNW1u"}
{"name":"Synweave Nightcamo Cloak","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/head/hood-cowl-mask-purple.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.RHVuWUgf9E3Cm8ur"}},"system":{"tier":2,"name":"","description":"","bulk":0.5,"charge":2,"class":"light","type":"improvised","properties":"","equipped":false,"armor":0,"ward":0,"evasion":2,"magicArmor":1,"quantity":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774473918036,"modifiedTime":1774473918036,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"vahtvQYmaxEcg95b"}
